author: Kynix @KynixXBT
text: $SPX almost at ATH. New ATH for Russell, new ATH for $XAU. Yet $BTC and $ETH are down today, dragging alts down with them. The discrepancy in Tradfi and Crypto is getting ridiculous. Either Crypto leads and we topped already or it lags behind + catches up. Betting on the latter.
